### ============================================================================
### TEST 2: Books Search - POST /search
### Testing Books category with OpenLibrary and Anna's Archive
### ============================================================================

### 2.1 Basic books search (category-based)
POST http://localhost:8000/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "python programming",
  "category": "books"
}

### 2.2 Search with OpenLibrary bang (!ol)
POST http://localhost:8000/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "!ol machine learning"
}

### 2.3 Search with Anna's Archive bang (!aa)
POST http://localhost:8000/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "!aa artificial intelligence"
}

### 2.4 Books search with pagination
POST http://localhost:8000/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "data science",
  "category": "books",
  "page": 6,
  "per_page": 100
}

### 2.5 OpenLibrary search with specific engine parameter
POST http://localhost:8000/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "javascript",
  "engine": "openlibrary",
  "page": 20,
  "per_page": 5
}

### 2.6 Anna's Archive search with specific engine parameter
POST http://localhost:8000/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "computer science",
  "engine": "annas archive",
  "page": 1,
  "per_page": 10
}

### 2.8 Search with !books category bang
POST http://localhost:8000/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "!books quantum physics"
}
